		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><font class="h1font"> Local Vancouver, Canada<br></font><br><font class="h2font"> <b>Overall Rating:</b> </font><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size='1'>(3.83)</font><br><font class="h2font"> <b>Author:</b> <A HREF='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=10500'>Charles "Kakita" Bickford</A></font><font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=10500&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a><br><font class="h2font"> <b>Date Submitted:</b> May 25, 2002</font><p align='justify'><blockquote><font class="bfont"> Well the day started late as we waited for the few regulars that said they were coming.<br>
<br>
1:00 pm<br>
Tournament starts<br>
First round play versus Ranger Choke / Moria swarm<br>
I bid 8 win the bid I start pony. Play sting exert frodo, Iplay aragorn and move twice see nothin special. He plays no stranger and aragorn&#39;s bow, moves to site 2 and stays after I drop nelya and exert to play the ford.<br>
I heal frodo, I exert frodo with sting he got nothin I jump to 4 he plays nothing so I move to 5 he plays balrog from deck I stealth and kill sam.( Not one fellowship card in hand other than sting and the stealth and I know this is gonna kick me in A$$ )<br>
He moves to 3 I play king he versatility&#39;s and bows 3 times assigns frodo and tries to power twice to bad bad for him that I had 2 all blades perish in hand.<br>
FW +3<br>
<br>
Highs <br>
quick game allowing me to run to subway<br>
<br>
Lows<br>
Hoped for a better game and my opponent got screwed<br>
<br>
round 2<br>
me versus a deck that I built for my friend (moria)<br>
I win bid play aragorn and map move twice using my sites I run over 2 runners.<br>
He plays alot ( Sam, gimli,arwen a elven bow on her, aragorn and his bow, gandalf)and moves to streets of bree leaving a total of 23 twilght for me to use I drop 2x black breath 2x not easily destroyed he moves on giving me another 8 twilght for a total of 27 twilght I drop king, play enque. Leaving a total of 18 twilight I enquea aragorn x3 then I use not easily destroyed healing enquea and do it to legolas x2 use not easily destroyed again to heal enquea and do it to gimli twice and then I relentless charge exerting king killing off legolas, arwen, and aragorn.<br>
He assigns king to gimli and enquea to pipin all die followed by gandalf and sam he stops.<br>
I move one site and stay after killin his attempted swarm and stay<br>
He moves forward I gate attea and win the game<br>
FW +3<br>
+6<br>
<br>
3rd round<br>
don&#39;t remember much I think he played celeborn and elrond and then i think he played galadriel I dropped nelya and enquea and that was that i think if I am wrong I appologize<br>
FW +3<br>
+9<br>
<br>
4th round<br>
me versus moria/sauron direct damage and archery<br>
bad game for my opponent he drew no minions til site 8 bad shuffling job. I walked to the end with no wounds other than my exertions to kill off his guys sorry bud bad game for you<br>
FW +3<br>
+12<br>
<br>
5th round mirror match<br>
me versus Andrew Walker #1 in Canada playing my deck (he copied it because his other decks just could not beat my speed fellowship)<br>
Good game all the way best part was site 9 he dropped king and cantea I bearly made it through but that is usualy how it ends in mirror matches any way.<br>
FW +3<br>
+15<br>
<br>
6th round<br>
me versus joel and his mighty nazgul<br>
I start move to 2 and then 3 he plays king at site 2 I versatility he loses king to archery exertions from lego.<br>
He moves I play nothing both times.<br>
I play arwen and boromir and aragorns bow, I move he plays a couple of nazguel and over whelms boromir and arwen took two wounds.<br>
He moves I drop cantea he exerts lego fully and aragorn twice (I all blades one of them) to kill cantea. He moves I drop king relentless charge twice and run over frodo<br>
FW +3<br>
+18<br>
<br>
With no loses I felt pretty good but then this deck has only lost 2 in tournament play with a record of 33-2 out side of tournament play it has a record of 55-4<br>
The following is my Deck hope you all enjoy it<br>
